Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:40.35,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.70,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Is she for sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:47.81,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,This is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:50.20,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.55,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,But, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:58.78,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be bringing your \Ndaughter to a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.65,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, she'll be running my gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.73,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,It's a learning experience for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.46,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you also choose one, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:11.94,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:14.86,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you find one you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:51.17,Default,W,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I didn't expect you \Nto actually select one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.30,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kumiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:58.02,Default,G,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That dream again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:57.96,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing what I can to track \Ndown the designer children...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.88,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't learn their current locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.13,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to rely on your power, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.76,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,She says we'll have to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,During the last battle, the Machine \NGoodfellow didn't activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.77,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei, you're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:18.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But Amarok and Malkin appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:23.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think one of the two remaining \Ndesigner children was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:27.77,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hana predicted the flow of Orgone energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,but the Machine Goodfellow didn't activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean something there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,other than Machine Goodfellows \Nuses Orgone energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Something felt different than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.88,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Pitz says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.33,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.98,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,He really is asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.25,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why not give him a goodnight kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.53,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.28,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.03,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.21,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.67,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:49.54,Default - italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really what the Japanese \Nindependent attack force should be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The wait is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:57.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is tonight's main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The challenger:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:02.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Asia's one surviving carnivorous dinosaur...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Zynus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How long will his win streak continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The undefeated emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,the champion of this arena...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:18.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.04,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fast... That was so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The massive Devil Zynus fell \Nin a mere ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds, and he's lying \Non the floor of the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:53.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The giant impact of the champion's right fist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:58.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,has slain the last living dinosaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.81,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Baku! Baku! Baku! Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Baku! Baku! Baku! Baku! Baku! Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:06.44,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1405,1)}Boys' Battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.64,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Baku, you don't have to keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.33,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Those are your father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.05,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do as he says...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:25.45,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.59,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.72,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,These fights are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:34.95,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:37.00,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.06,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.30,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,You have a fiancé, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:47.24,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.29,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.05,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.62,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,They say this mascot will help you sleep at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.47,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,It matches mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.47,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.34,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:13.55,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,holding on to it can really keep bad dreams away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.57,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:20.72,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a little childish, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.62,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You were wonderful out there tonight, Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,With you around, we make \Nlots of money in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:35.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But the money you earn, and you, \Nboth belong to the Asanoda Yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that your grades are good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful to the lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's allowing you to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.93,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go home, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:53.59,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go alone. Leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:13.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are always eating something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.99,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a pool around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go swimming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.85,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:26.09,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to pace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.29,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Pace yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:50.89,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Keep looking ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.45,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever kissed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.96,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:02.20,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.03,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.87,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not yet... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.97,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.42,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,They look so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:34.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Kiltgangs come to \NEarth, everyone's gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:39.07,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let that happen. No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.49,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? This is Manatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.81,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,How is the town looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:50.38,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't found anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.57,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I found something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.96,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending the information now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:59.47,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,There's an illegal underground arena in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.55,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,An underground arena?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.93,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,They hold unauthorized fighting tournaments,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:09.49,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,and the audience bets on the winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.33,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.63,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I'll send agents from \Nanother team there—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, the Midsummer's Knights will go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:21.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We need to handle stuff like that ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.75,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.96,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.83,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.42,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.91,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.88,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:41.13,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,That little mascot charm \Nyou gave Baku last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:48.56,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that it brings deep \Nsleep with no nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.57,0:11:53.27,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to have a mascot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.72,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,that matches yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.86,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:03.71,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really a mascot that prevents \Nyou from having nightmares?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.99,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,If there is, I'd like one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.20,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.78,Default,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... Do you have an invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.69,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:49.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Minors are not permitted here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.75,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Will this suffice to change your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We're here for... educational purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:03.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Go in, then... I hope you learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.63,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,This has happened before, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The wait is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is tonight's main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's challenger:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Northern Hemisphere's \Nultimate murder weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Gimerock Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And facing him is the man you all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:56.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The fighting prince of the arena,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,the champion, Baku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you betting on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What are the odds on the champion tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,1.2 to 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:16.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right... I'm in for 2,000,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You have guts, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:21.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Come on, champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:28.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the real reason you wanted to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He opens up with a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:39.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But any non-ranged weapon is allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:43.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The murder weapon's blade slices back and forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:46.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Will it strike his prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.25,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Baku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:04.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:08.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Once more, Baku's fists explode into the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Northern Hemisphere's \Nultimate murder weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:13.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,was no match for the invincible champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:19.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This is a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:24.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Our arena always welcomes surprise challengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the first night we've actually had one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:32.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell us your name, hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Amara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.78,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Amarok...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:46.54,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Teppei,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.30,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.82,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Ranged weapons are against the rules, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:11.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Our brave challenger's name is Amara!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:16.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Amara and the champion, Baku, \Nare staring each other down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:19.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The tension is immense...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.10,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories, Bugbear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.94,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I remember when we used to play like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:21.30,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Is this an earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.82,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Bugbear's heart is causing space itself to shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on the emergency lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:42.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Baku, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.42,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Amarok...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:07.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:15.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What? It isn't Bugbear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.50,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.91,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.99,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,I think his name was Kariya Haruhiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:28.43,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,He was at the casino where I worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:31.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Zin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:35.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you were working with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.76,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,Those iron pipes leaning against \Nthat wall over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:41.34,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,They're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:46.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You know you have to pay for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:49.79,Default,J,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you that they're dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.03,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.45,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:29.23,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you aren't very friendly, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:35.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's standing here alone, \Nand you just walk by?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:38.48,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Are you with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.52,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,With him? It's more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're bound by fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:45.53,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:48.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You could say we're scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.70,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like hitting women.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.00,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.65,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Don't destroy who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what we're here to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:06.47,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't hit women.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:08.84,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Ranged weapons are against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Bugbear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.47,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:19.69,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And I was going to show him a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.85,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sir... Sir... Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His pupils are dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't breathing, and we can't get a pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:36.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to wait for a doctor \Nto say for sure, but he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:42.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,His heart stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:54.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I am immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.74,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,If Amarok and Malkin were there, \Nthen the one we're looking for was, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.34,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.37,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:12.58,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,This time without Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Want my chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:18.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:25.05,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I looked into the Asanoda Yakuza when \NI checked out the underground arena...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Magus incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:11.39,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're sweating terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:13.60,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:19.56,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, am I really the one you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:24.48,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:43.04,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Don't destroy who I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:15.89,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,We were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:20.64,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,The new member of the Planetary Gears \Nis Baku, the boy from the arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:25.40,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,But Baku instinctively fears contact \Nwith Amarok and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.29,0:24:29.61,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Will he pilot his Machine Goodfellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:33.99,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on episode 13 of {\i1}Captain Earth{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:35.36,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,My Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:35.99,Title2,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,My Town
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.99,0:24:38.41,Default,Narr,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine, scramble!
